msgctxt "mn41:43.1"
msgid "Ākaṅkheyya ce, gahapatayo, dhammacārī samacārī: "
msgstr "A person of principled and moral conduct might wish: "

msgctxt "mn41:43.2"
msgid "‘aho vatāhaṃ āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyyan’ti; "
msgstr "‘If only I might realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with my own insight due to the ending of defilements.’ "

msgctxt "mn41:43.3"
msgid "ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ vijjati, yaṃ so āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyya. "
